<h1><a id="NuChange__ToA_Redifining_Transfer_of_Accountability_0"></a>NuChange - ToA: Redifining Transfer of Accountability</h1>
<p>Communication of information between nurses, especially during change of shifts is vital in patient care. NuChange TOA aids this communication by providing a spreadsheet like application that <strong>syncs in real time</strong> between systems loggedin as same generic user. It is ideal for projecting on to smart-boards.  NuChange TOA incorporates “S.A.F.E.” reporting process: Story, Assessment, Follow-up, and Evaluation.</p>
